      "content": "hey i just landed in dubai from a 14 hour flight and my chest feels really sharp and painful whenever i breathe in deep. i'm also kinda short of breath. i've been super stressed with work lately and the travel has been crazy... do u think this is just a panic attack or something? i'm feeling really anxious about it.",
