      "content": "idk i dont really want to go to an er if i can help it... hospitals here are crazy expensive and i just want to get to my hotel. i've had these weird feelings before when i'm stressed and they always just pass once i sit down and relax. do u really think it's that serious? maybe if i just do some deep breathing exercises and take some calming tea it'll go away?",
